A cikin binciken da aka yi a shekara ta 2014 na Ƙungiyar Ƙwarewa da Aiki ta Ƙasar Ingila, an gano cewa kashi 17 cikin ɗari na rashin aikin yi ya samo asali ne daga matsalar harshe.
