HIV/Aids: Ƙaruwar kashi 14% a ƙasar Sin
China ta ce adadin mutanen da ke fama da cutar HIV da Aids a duniya ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Masu kula da aikin gwamnati sun ce adadin masu cutar a ƙasar ya kai 820,000.
An samu karin mutane 40,000 da suka kamu da cutar a farkon 2018.
Sun lura cewa mutane suna kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, kuma wannan ya bambanta da yadda suke zuwa.
An lura cewa cutar HIV ta bazu cikin sauri a wasu biranen ƙasar Sin ta wurin ƙarin jini.
A wani taron da aka yi a birnin Yunnan, likitocin ƙasar Sin sun ce ba a yawan samun cutar ta wannan hanyar.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV da kuma AIDS yana ƙaruwa da kusan mutane 100,000.
A ƙasar Sin, mutane da yawa da suke da cutar HIV suna da dangantaka da maza da mata.
A shekara ta 1997 ne aka amince da auren jinsi ɗaya a ƙasar Sin, amma mutane da yawa suna nuna bambancin ra'ayi game da jima'i.
Amma, a cikin al'umma, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke so su yi jima'i da maza za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna zuwa ne daga lalata da ba a kafa doka game da yadda za a kāre irin wannan dangantaka ba.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin ƙasar Sin ta yi alkawarin ba da taimako kyauta ga marasa lafiya da ke da cutar HIV don magance matsalar rashin ji.
