Menene bikin Global Citizen Festival kuma me ya sa aka yi hakan?
A kowace ranar Asabar a birnin New York, za a yi bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara da ke ɗauke da manyan mawaƙa, kuma babban jigonsa shi ne bikin safiya a duniya.
Bikin na Global Citizen ya cika shekaru bakwai kuma ana sa ran dubban mutane za su taru a Central Park Great Lawn, ba wai kawai don ganin fitattun mawaƙa kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da babban burin bikin na kawar da rashin ruwa kafin 2030.
An kafa bikin na Global Citizen a shekarar 2012 a matsayin wani shiri na Global Poverty Project, wanda ke da alhakin kafa wata kungiya da kuma samar da hanyoyin da za a magance talauci ta hanyar daukar nauyin mutane da yawa don yin gwagwarmaya.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don wani taro (sai dai idan mutum yana da ikon biyan kuɗin tikitin VIP), dole ne ya yi wani aikin sa kai, ya aika wa wani mai sarauta a duniya da imel, ya yi wani abu ko kuma ya yi wani tallace-tallace don waɗannan manyan mutane su san ainihin manufar shirin.
Da yake shekara 12 kawai ke nan kafin ƙarshen wannan zamanin, za ka iya yin mamaki ko Global Citizen ta yi nasara a aikinta?
Shin nuna goyon baya a taron nishaɗi kyauta hanya ce ta jawo hankalin mutane su yi gwagwarmaya da matsalar ko kuwa wani abu ne da ba zai yiwu ba, kuma mutane suna nuna cewa suna kawo canji mai girma ta hanyar yin amfani da takardu ko kuma yin tweet game da manufar?
A shekara ta 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya ga mutane fiye da miliyan 19 da suka ba da shawarwari game da ayyukan agaji.
Ya ce, wadannan manufofi sun ba shugabannin duniya mamaki kuma sun yi watsi da shirin ci gaban da aka yi hasashen zai kai dala biliyan 37 da za su amfana da mutane biliyan 2.25 a 2030.
