Ƙungiyar ta kuma lura cewa kuɗin da aka samu ya canja rayuwar mutane 649 a dukan duniya.
Wata kungiya mai suna The Power of Nutrition a Birtaniya ta hada kai da wasu masu ba da tallafi don taimakawa yara su girma lafiya. Sun yi alkawarin bada dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda, don magance matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar. Wannan ya faru ne sakamakon sakonnin Global Citizens 4,700 da aka samu a yanar gizo.
Tare da taimakon kungiyoyin agaji na Burtaniya, gwamnatoci da Global Citizen, zaku iya magance matsalar karancin abinci mai gina jiki a duniya, in ji Tracey Ullman, mai ba da shawara kan samar da abinci mai gina jiki, a wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an ɗauki matakai fiye da 5,000, an yi kira ga gwamnatin Burtaniya don ta taimaka wa mata da yara. Gwamnati ta sanar da gaggawa kuma Power of Nutrition ta taimaka wa mata da yara miliyan 5 ta hanyar rarraba abinci.
